room_title: Escape room "Revenger's Rescue" by NWA Escape Room in Fayetteville (AR)
room_description: The powerful protectors of earth, the mighty Revengers, have been captured! It's up to you and your team to get into Star Tower to find the precious and powerful "eternity stones" which can defeat their enemy and guarantee the heroes' release. You will only have about 60 minutes to find them and escape back to HQ. Can you prove your skills and find the stones in time?
